'''Grum''' is a man who runs [[Grum's Gold Exchange]] in [[Port Sarim]]. He buys and sells unenchanted [[ring]]s, [[amulet]]s and [[necklace]]s from sapphire up to diamond.

During the [[Merlin's Crystal]] [[Quests|quest]], players will have to bring a loaf of [[bread]] to his gold exchange and give it to a beggar in order to receive the [[Excalibur]] from [[The Lady of the Lake]].

